reviewText: An absolutely outstanding review of what is going on in our world and more distinctly, our nation, today. It will give you the information you will need to answer the question "What is happening in our country...has everyone gone mad?" No, they aren't mad, they're just focused on their own goals; goals that are as evil as they are real. I highly recommend it to all who want the truth of those who seek to rule over us.
